<# Important Notes (Category: Replays)                                                                           |
    This API is called when a player opens their Arena battle logs. This API query should place data
in the replay and players table. This information should also fill in a seperate set of fields in the player
database allowing the extension to track the latest Grand Arena team used by the defending player for
future reference. We will want our extension to be able to query what is the current Arena defense
team being used by a current player so it should be a constantly updating data value

    ! Note: Because Arena and Grand Arena attacks always use a players current heroes, the player table
    !       only needs to point to the players own heroes and will only need to keep track of the team
    !       composition and patronages. From this we will want to build a module that can be used to
    !       query a team to sim against.

This API is Exportable: No

Long Term goals (Out of Scope of this project)
    This information will be used to identify counters to teams and will keep track of specific teams
defense rates. This information will go a long way in allowing players to optimize their arena defenses.

Note for extension developer
 1. None

#>
